description:
The Electoral Boundaries data shows the boundaries of the Legislative Assembly
electorates of Brindabella, Ginninderra and Molonglo as determined by the augmented Australian Capital Territory Electoral Commission pursuant to section 35 of the Electoral Act 1992.
